data.title: Jane Child - Jane Child Album
data.meta_description: Jane Child is the debut album by Canadian singer Jane Child, released in 1989 on the Warner Bros. record label. It includes the single "Don't Wanna Fall in Love", which reached number two on the US Billboard Hot 100 and number 22 in the UK Singles Chart. The album reached number 49 on the US Billboard 200 chart for the chart week of April 28, 1990.
